<div><span style=3D"font-size: 16px;"><strong>Welcome to Snyk! </strong></s=
pan><br /><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br />With your free account you can find =
and automatically fix vulnerabilities in your code, open source dependencie=
s, containers, and infrastructure as code &mdash; all powered by Snyk&rsquo=
;s industry-leading security intelligence.<br />&nbsp;</div>
<div>To get started we recommend following these steps to find and fix your=
 first vulnerabilities:</div>
<ol>
<li><strong>Import your repositories</strong> with one-click (GitHub, GitLa=
b, &amp; more)</li>
<li><strong>Scan projects </strong>for vulns in your packages and dependenc=
ies</li>
<li><strong>Review suggested fixes</strong> including automated fix pull re=
quests</li>
<li><strong>Merge fixes</strong> and carry on<br /></li>
</ol>
